text: The Archbishop's Palace of Alcalá de Henares (Spanish: Palacio Arzobispal de Alcalá de Henares) is a palace in Alcalá de Henares, Spain. It was listed as a Spanish Property of Cultural Interest in 1931. File:Constantin Uhde (1888) Escalera de Covarrubias en el Palacio Arzobispal de Alcalá de Henares.png|Steps of Covarrubias.
